WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:00:13.598 --> 00:00:15.474
I lost the teleportation stone.

3
00:00:16.058 --> 00:00:17.685
I don't have the time to look for it.

4
00:00:17.768 --> 00:00:19.895
I'll have to defeat them all.

5
00:00:20.479 --> 00:00:22.356
otherwise. I can't make it out alive.

6
00:00:27.778 --> 00:00:29.447
My body is exhausted.

7
00:00:29.530 --> 00:00:30.990
I can't use Stealth or Murderous Intent.

8
00:00:33.784 --> 00:00:34.702
But even so.

9
00:00:35.494 --> 00:00:36.746
I cannot give up.

10
00:00:38.914 --> 00:00:39.749
I must...

11
00:00:40.499 --> 00:00:41.751
Survive!

12
00:00:49.008 --> 00:00:50.843
Because I've always been weak.

13
00:00:51.636 --> 00:00:53.554
I understand the sorrow of the weak
better than anyone else.

14
00:00:54.138 --> 00:00:57.016
But still. I desire to climb to the top.

15
00:01:09.654 --> 00:01:13.324
That kid has a nickname.
The Weakest Hunter of All Mankind.

16
00:01:16.744 --> 00:01:18.663
The weakest? Not the strongest?

17
00:01:20.539 --> 00:01:21.457
The weakest.

18
00:01:21.540 --> 00:01:24.418
He was even injured in an E-Rank
dungeon and hospitalized.

19
00:01:25.169 --> 00:01:27.505
He's probably the weakest hunter.

20
00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:30.925
Sung.

21
00:01:31.008 --> 00:01:31.967
It's enough.

22
00:01:32.051 --> 00:01:33.511
Don't push yourself anymore.

23
00:01:33.594 --> 00:01:35.805
That's right. Jinwoo.

24
00:01:35.888 --> 00:01:37.431
It's better to give up now.

25
00:01:41.977 --> 00:01:43.354
It's your own fault.

26
00:01:47.274 --> 00:01:50.403
Why do you always love to take risks?

27
00:01:51.112 --> 00:01:53.906
As an E-rank hunter. you should be content

28
00:01:54.532 --> 00:01:56.367
to have grown this much.

29
00:01:57.243 --> 00:01:58.452
Shouldn't you?

30
00:01:59.328 --> 00:02:00.287
Jinwoo.

31
00:03:33.589 --> 00:03:35.591
The third Jeju Island raid mission.

32
00:03:36.634 --> 00:03:40.304
At that time. I was unable to fight.

33
00:03:40.387 --> 00:03:42.348
so I couldn't participate.

34
00:03:43.349 --> 00:03:45.267
You participated. right?

35
00:03:45.893 --> 00:03:49.063
Yes. My mission was to relay orders
and be on the outer guard.

36
00:03:50.064 --> 00:03:52.650
There were many casualties.

37
00:03:53.150 --> 00:03:56.821
Those who returned alive
have indelible traumas.

38
00:03:58.364 --> 00:04:00.032
Any hunter

39
00:04:00.116 --> 00:04:02.118
would have such experiences.

40
00:04:03.285 --> 00:04:05.746
However. if we cannot overcome the trauma.

41
00:04:05.830 --> 00:04:07.373
what awaits us

42
00:04:07.456 --> 00:04:08.999
is death.

43
00:04:10.584 --> 00:04:13.420
By the way. is this person really me?

44
00:04:13.504 --> 00:04:14.964
'I' seem completely different.

45
00:04:15.631 --> 00:04:17.550
Not only taller. but also stronger.

46
00:04:18.134 --> 00:04:19.009
'I' feel very strong.

47
00:04:20.344 --> 00:04:22.513
But the change is only on the outside.

48
00:04:22.596 --> 00:04:24.598
'I' am still weak inside.

49
00:04:25.266 --> 00:04:26.934
'I' am about to lose my life again.

50
00:04:32.148 --> 00:04:34.275
E-rank hunter Sung Jinwoo.

51
00:04:34.817 --> 00:04:36.694
This is what you are.

52
00:04:37.695 --> 00:04:39.613
Reckless and unaware of your position.

53
00:04:40.239 --> 00:04:41.323
Shut up.

54
00:04:55.171 --> 00:04:56.338
You have a long way to go.

55
00:04:56.839 --> 00:04:58.799
You talked about
your realization to act cool.

56
00:04:58.883 --> 00:05:00.759
That's why you ended up like this.

57
00:05:01.385 --> 00:05:04.221
You are the one who killed yourself.

58
00:05:06.265 --> 00:05:08.475
In the end... nothing changed?

59
00:05:09.268 --> 00:05:10.728
Just like that time.

60
00:05:13.522 --> 00:05:16.192
What happened after that?

61
00:05:18.444 --> 00:05:19.820
Eh?

62
00:05:21.864 --> 00:05:23.991
This quest is over?

63
00:05:24.575 --> 00:05:26.660
Is this what
'Luck is also a strength' means?

64
00:05:28.287 --> 00:05:31.290
It seems that you are not to die here.

65
00:05:32.082 --> 00:05:33.167
See you next time.

66
00:05:45.721 --> 00:05:46.805
This is

67
00:05:47.765 --> 00:05:49.224
the Penalty Zone.

68
00:05:51.644 --> 00:05:53.228
I remember now.

69
00:05:53.312 --> 00:05:56.065
I haven't completed my daily quest today.

70
00:05:58.108 --> 00:05:59.777
No matter what.

71
00:06:02.655 --> 00:06:04.156
nice timing.

72
00:06:04.823 --> 00:06:06.367
Thanks to this. I survived.

73
00:06:07.326 --> 00:06:09.078
It wishes me good luck?

74
00:06:09.912 --> 00:06:12.957
It means this quest is hard enough
to wish me good luck.

75
00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:16.585
Or maybe it wants to cheer me on.

76
00:06:17.378 --> 00:06:18.420
Whatever.

77
00:06:18.504 --> 00:06:19.588
Store.

78
00:06:21.298 --> 00:06:23.842
This is the first time
my fatigue level has exceeded 90.

79
00:06:32.309 --> 00:06:33.352
Hmm?

80
00:06:33.435 --> 00:06:34.853
In a critical state.

81
00:06:34.937 --> 00:06:37.189
even potions can't restore HP?

82
00:06:38.524 --> 00:06:40.484
I'll have to let it recover naturally

83
00:06:40.567 --> 00:06:43.195
or automatically when I level up.

84
00:06:44.697 --> 00:06:47.324
It seems I worried for nothing.

85
00:06:52.579 --> 00:06:54.331
See you next time?

86
00:06:55.666 --> 00:06:56.625
Sure.

87
00:06:56.709 --> 00:06:58.919
If I can survive. let's meet again.

88
00:06:59.420 --> 00:07:01.547
If you can't kill me.

89
00:07:01.630 --> 00:07:03.841
this pain

90
00:07:03.924 --> 00:07:06.176
will only make me stronger.

91
00:07:21.900 --> 00:07:23.861
I had a strange dream.

92
00:07:25.654 --> 00:07:26.488
Hmm?

93
00:07:26.572 --> 00:07:29.616
Brother is still not back?

94
00:07:29.700 --> 00:07:32.953
Is he working this late?

95
00:07:33.996 --> 00:07:36.206
Maybe he has a girlfriend?

96
00:07:36.749 --> 00:07:38.459
That's impossible.

97
00:07:39.376 --> 00:07:42.254
I told him there'd be
a parent-teacher meeting today.

98
00:07:42.838 --> 00:07:44.923
He should come in time.

99
00:07:50.763 --> 00:07:53.640
It's great that I can recover
when leveling up.

100
00:07:55.225 --> 00:07:57.311
There's over 10 minutes left.

101
00:07:58.062 --> 00:07:59.313
I'll use the time

102
00:07:59.396 --> 00:08:00.856
to prepare my equipment.

103
00:08:02.733 --> 00:08:03.567
{\an8}Hmm?

104
00:08:04.485 --> 00:08:05.319
Purchase.

105
00:08:10.824 --> 00:08:12.242
Knight Killer.

106
00:08:12.326 --> 00:08:15.621
Increases damage to
armor-type monsters by 25 percent.

107
00:08:15.704 --> 00:08:17.539
It's expensive but useful.

108
00:08:18.207 --> 00:08:19.917
Next is this one.

109
00:08:20.584 --> 00:08:22.753
The rune stone I obtained
when I killed Igris.

110
00:08:23.420 --> 00:08:25.506
This should also be useful.

111
00:08:38.102 --> 00:08:39.895
Ruler's Hand.

112
00:08:39.978 --> 00:08:41.647
A skill that doesn't consume MP?

113
00:08:41.730 --> 00:08:42.940
Seems quite handy.

114
00:08:43.607 --> 00:08:47.361
It can physically manipulate objects
without touching them.

115
00:08:47.861 --> 00:08:49.071
Like that move?

116
00:08:55.744 --> 00:08:58.372
I can't move objects that are too large.

117
00:09:00.582 --> 00:09:02.835
That's probably all the preparations
I can make.

118
00:09:06.213 --> 00:09:08.006
The rest is up to luck.

119
00:09:16.098 --> 00:09:19.476
A few hours apart and your
numbers have increased a lot.

120
00:09:26.066 --> 00:09:29.486
Approaching the Jeju Island
air defense zone.

121
00:09:29.570 --> 00:09:30.737
Understood.

122
00:09:31.280 --> 00:09:32.656
Sorry.

123
00:09:32.739 --> 00:09:35.284
This must be very uncomfortable for you.

124
00:09:35.367 --> 00:09:36.201
No.

125
00:09:36.285 --> 00:09:37.828
I'm fine.

126
00:09:37.911 --> 00:09:42.791
Although I wasn't a hunter yet
during the third Jeju Island raid.

127
00:09:42.875 --> 00:09:45.627
I can understand your feelings.

128
00:09:45.711 --> 00:09:48.005
I'm grateful to hear that.

129
00:09:48.088 --> 00:09:49.089
Mr. Choi.

130
00:09:49.173 --> 00:09:50.924
A faint mana reaction
has been detected at sea.

131
00:09:51.008 --> 00:09:52.593
Please check the screen.

132
00:09:56.680 --> 00:09:57.723
This is...

133
00:10:03.061 --> 00:10:05.147
This Knight Killer is quite useful.

134
00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:06.940
Much better than fighting with bare hands.

135
00:10:07.566 --> 00:10:08.400
But...

136
00:10:08.484 --> 00:10:10.527
What's with this strange feeling?

137
00:10:10.611 --> 00:10:12.362
I've defeated so many.
yet there's no progress at all.

138
00:10:12.446 --> 00:10:14.573
There's no sign of leveling up.

139
00:10:15.199 --> 00:10:16.033
Moreover.

140
00:10:16.700 --> 00:10:18.785
what is that Mage doing?

141
00:10:18.869 --> 00:10:21.663
He's been chanting spells.
but not launching any attacks at me.

142
00:10:21.747 --> 00:10:23.540
Only these Knights are attacking.

143
00:10:23.624 --> 00:10:25.334
What are they doing?

144
00:10:26.752 --> 00:10:27.586
The gate.

145
00:10:27.669 --> 00:10:28.712
Is it summoning magic?

146
00:10:28.795 --> 00:10:30.964
These Knights are summoned

147
00:10:31.048 --> 00:10:32.674
as weapons.

148
00:10:32.758 --> 00:10:34.927
So even if I defeat them.
I won't earn any points.

149
00:10:35.802 --> 00:10:36.970
My target should be

150
00:10:37.054 --> 00:10:38.263
the Mages

151
00:10:38.347 --> 00:10:39.681
which means you!

152
00:10:46.563 --> 00:10:47.773
I was right.

153
00:10:47.856 --> 00:10:49.691
The target should be the Mages.

154
00:10:50.526 --> 00:10:51.777
Since I figured this out...

155
00:10:53.403 --> 00:10:55.030
Five left.

156
00:10:58.992 --> 00:11:00.077
Four left.

157
00:11:17.386 --> 00:11:19.888
How long do you plan to hide behind them?

158
00:11:25.686 --> 00:11:26.561
Three to go.

159
00:11:34.236 --> 00:11:35.279
Golems?

160
00:11:51.420 --> 00:11:54.631
You are collecting the Knights' power
to summon a powerful beast.

161
00:11:55.757 --> 00:11:58.719
However. the fewer the Knights.
the easier it is to find you.

162
00:12:14.943 --> 00:12:17.446
The Mage who summoned you disappeared.

163
00:12:18.613 --> 00:12:20.282
So you should

164
00:12:21.491 --> 00:12:24.786
go to hell!

165
00:12:50.479 --> 00:12:52.689
It's over.

166
00:12:52.773 --> 00:12:54.316
What's next?

167
00:12:55.025 --> 00:12:57.110
The more points obtained.

168
00:12:57.194 --> 00:13:00.697
the higher the chance of changing
to a high-ranked job.

169
00:13:01.406 --> 00:13:03.825
The system will analyze
the player's actions in the quest

170
00:13:03.909 --> 00:13:06.078
and assign a corresponding job.

171
00:13:06.161 --> 00:13:07.287
Can't I choose for myself?

172
00:13:16.338 --> 00:13:18.215
Eh? What does this mean?

173
00:13:33.605 --> 00:13:35.690
Shadow Army?

174
00:13:36.983 --> 00:13:37.859
Eh?

175
00:13:38.360 --> 00:13:40.404
Wait a minute. what's this?

176
00:13:40.487 --> 00:13:43.115
This... is my job?

177
00:13:44.491 --> 00:13:46.118
Necromancer?

178
00:13:46.201 --> 00:13:47.285
Hold on...

179
00:13:47.369 --> 00:13:50.080
My intelligence has hardly developed.

180
00:13:50.163 --> 00:13:51.456
How can this be?

181
00:13:52.457 --> 00:13:54.042
The Necromancer is a magical profession

182
00:13:54.126 --> 00:13:58.213
capable of summoning undead beasts
and controlling them in battle.

183
00:13:59.214 --> 00:14:01.049
I am an Assassin-type hunter

184
00:14:01.133 --> 00:14:03.176
with a close-quarters combat style.

185
00:14:03.260 --> 00:14:05.345
My improvements focused on strength.

186
00:14:05.429 --> 00:14:06.680
my skills too.

187
00:14:07.264 --> 00:14:09.724
If I change my job to a Necromancer.
a back-line profession.

188
00:14:09.808 --> 00:14:11.560
all the abilities I've gained
will be useless.

189
00:14:12.477 --> 00:14:14.521
Yes or No?

190
00:14:14.604 --> 00:14:16.106
So I can reject it?

191
00:14:16.189 --> 00:14:18.483
Changing to necromancer

192
00:14:18.567 --> 00:14:20.235
is too risky. and the reward is uncertain.

193
00:14:20.819 --> 00:14:21.945
No.

194
00:14:23.155 --> 00:14:24.865
Hidden class?

195
00:14:31.288 --> 00:14:34.458
Does this mean the profession
has special abilities?

196
00:14:37.002 --> 00:14:38.503
Necromancer.

197
00:14:38.587 --> 00:14:40.922
If only I could experience
its abilities first.

198
00:14:44.676 --> 00:14:46.052
Summoning magic.

199
00:14:46.136 --> 00:14:47.429
That's right.

200
00:14:47.512 --> 00:14:50.015
The summoning magic used by these Mages

201
00:14:50.098 --> 00:14:53.351
resembles the Necromancers' abilities.

202
00:14:53.935 --> 00:14:55.729
And all my battles here

203
00:14:55.812 --> 00:14:58.565
are like a review of past battles.

204
00:14:59.566 --> 00:15:02.986
The sound of "job change"
made me think I had a choice.

205
00:15:03.069 --> 00:15:04.613
But it was all prearranged?

206
00:15:05.155 --> 00:15:06.573
Is the system playing tricks?

207
00:15:07.741 --> 00:15:08.950
But it's quite interesting.

208
00:15:09.618 --> 00:15:11.995
These Mages had no combat ability.

209
00:15:12.496 --> 00:15:13.914
but I do.

210
00:15:14.414 --> 00:15:17.417
No one says Necromancers
can't fight on the front lines.

211
00:15:18.084 --> 00:15:20.504
If the profession is part
of the ability stats.

212
00:15:20.587 --> 00:15:23.673
it will be strengthened
with leveling up like the skills.

213
00:15:24.216 --> 00:15:27.886
And the undead army
may also grow stronger.

214
00:15:28.470 --> 00:15:29.471
This means...

215
00:15:30.055 --> 00:15:32.390
From now on.
it won't be just me leveling up.

216
00:15:33.266 --> 00:15:34.810
Well then.

217
00:15:40.941 --> 00:15:41.775
Please.

218
00:15:41.858 --> 00:15:43.151
Thank you.

219
00:15:47.405 --> 00:15:49.115
It's almost dawn.

220
00:15:49.699 --> 00:15:53.411
Hunter Cui and the others should
be arriving on the island soon.

221
00:15:53.495 --> 00:15:54.704
Hmm.

222
00:15:54.788 --> 00:15:56.331
Sorry for keeping you up so late.

223
00:15:56.414 --> 00:15:57.249
It's nothing.

224
00:15:57.749 --> 00:15:59.459
Now that you've stayed.

225
00:15:59.543 --> 00:16:02.420
are you up for a chat?

226
00:17:00.854 --> 00:17:02.480
Shadow Monarch?

227
00:17:02.981 --> 00:17:04.691
I had a second job change?

228
00:17:04.774 --> 00:17:07.068
Did I get so many points?

229
00:17:08.320 --> 00:17:11.781
Acquired job skills
and ability points +10.

230
00:17:11.865 --> 00:17:13.325
I also received a title.

231
00:17:13.992 --> 00:17:16.161
Since the reward has been delivered.

232
00:17:16.244 --> 00:17:17.662
does that mean this quest is over?

233
00:17:18.371 --> 00:17:20.373
So... I've completed the job change?

234
00:17:23.376 --> 00:17:25.545
I can hear them making sounds like screams

235
00:17:26.254 --> 00:17:29.090
as if expressing their pain.

236
00:17:30.258 --> 00:17:31.301
Shadow Extraction.

237
00:17:33.595 --> 00:17:35.347
A command word.

238
00:17:39.684 --> 00:17:40.685
Arise.

239
00:17:59.371 --> 00:18:01.206
This is amazing.

240
00:18:01.915 --> 00:18:04.793
Exclusive skill 'Shadow Extraction'.

241
00:18:04.876 --> 00:18:06.711
And 'Shadow Storage'?

242
00:18:06.795 --> 00:18:09.673
I can extract MP
and create Shadow Soldiers

243
00:18:09.756 --> 00:18:12.968
and summon or absord them anytime.

244
00:18:13.802 --> 00:18:16.638
So they are the Shadow Soldiers?

245
00:18:17.514 --> 00:18:22.227
Their postmortem interval and strength
will affect the skill's failure rate.

246
00:18:22.310 --> 00:18:23.812
I should take note of that.

247
00:18:24.980 --> 00:18:26.898
Besides Knights. there are also Mages.

248
00:18:26.982 --> 00:18:29.484
They even have their own levels.

249
00:18:31.319 --> 00:18:34.489
If I could extract A-rank
or S-rank shadows

250
00:18:34.572 --> 00:18:35.824
and their abilities stats

251
00:18:35.907 --> 00:18:38.410
are the same as before their death...

252
00:18:48.336 --> 00:18:49.713
Okay.

253
00:18:50.296 --> 00:18:53.008
There is a limit to the number
of soldiers I can keep.

254
00:18:53.842 --> 00:18:55.552
Eleven shadow soldiers.
extraction released.

255
00:18:57.762 --> 00:18:58.930
Sorry for waking you up.

256
00:19:00.682 --> 00:19:01.641
Alright.

257
00:19:02.225 --> 00:19:04.394
Blood-Red Commander Igris.

258
00:19:04.978 --> 00:19:07.105
If I could bring him under my command...

259
00:19:08.606 --> 00:19:09.566
Arise.

260
00:19:18.616 --> 00:19:20.118
What?

261
00:19:23.038 --> 00:19:25.290
Is this the situation mentioned earlier?

262
00:19:26.833 --> 00:19:28.209
Two more times.

263
00:19:32.839 --> 00:19:33.757
Arise.

264
00:19:39.637 --> 00:19:40.722
Damn.

265
00:19:41.306 --> 00:19:43.266
I don't have to explain.

266
00:19:43.349 --> 00:19:46.561
As hunters. without a second awakening.

267
00:19:46.644 --> 00:19:50.106
our abilities will stay
the same in our lifetime.

268
00:19:50.190 --> 00:19:53.276
That's why we practice martial arts
and call upon companions.

269
00:19:54.694 --> 00:19:56.237
Are you waiting for your king to return?

270
00:19:57.155 --> 00:19:59.324
The king who may not return at all.

271
00:20:00.492 --> 00:20:02.368
Commander Igris.

272
00:20:02.452 --> 00:20:03.661
You are a warrior.

273
00:20:04.454 --> 00:20:06.915
Wielding your sword against enemies
must be your inner desire.

274
00:20:08.083 --> 00:20:11.586
Do you want to let your sword
rot in such a desolate place?

275
00:20:13.505 --> 00:20:16.299
If you need someone
to wield your sword for.

276
00:20:17.092 --> 00:20:17.926
fight for me.

277
00:20:19.219 --> 00:20:21.846
Don't guard that empty throne.

278
00:20:22.514 --> 00:20:24.516
Protect me. who stand before you.

279
00:20:25.683 --> 00:20:26.601
Arise.

280
00:20:39.781 --> 00:20:40.782
But.

281
00:20:41.658 --> 00:20:43.743
I too occasionally dream of...

282
00:20:56.214 --> 00:21:01.553
... the awakened that keeps
appearing in this world.

283
00:21:03.138 --> 00:21:03.972
Isn't that obvious?

284
00:21:05.473 --> 00:21:07.016
Igris.

285
00:21:08.601 --> 00:21:10.478
This is your name.

286
00:21:11.980 --> 00:21:13.273
I hope that among them

287
00:21:14.149 --> 00:21:20.280
there will be one who possesses
a power with the brilliance of hope.

288
00:21:20.363 --> 00:21:23.867
Perhaps he is awakening
at this very moment.

289
00:21:39.215 --> 00:21:40.383
Nice to meet you.

290
00:23:19.857 --> 00:23:21.442
Mr. Choi.

291
00:23:21.526 --> 00:23:22.944
What is this?

292
00:23:23.027 --> 00:23:24.195
I don't know either.

293
00:23:24.278 --> 00:23:27.407
As far as I know.
such a thing shouldn't be here.

294
00:23:27.949 --> 00:23:29.200
However.

295
00:23:29.283 --> 00:23:30.326
it appears to be...

296
00:23:32.704 --> 00:23:34.163
They have evolved.

